              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28382942/" class="">一项关于死亡的集体表象的研究</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mengdom/" class=" " title="Aria-EZLN">Aria-EZLN</a>
                (采薇山阿)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28382942">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28382942/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p28382942-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">  二元对立的思维方式决定中间状态成为“禁忌”。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-02 01:29</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p28382942-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div> 二元对立的思维方式决定中间状态成为“禁忌”。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







